    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#### Espresso (Version 1)\r\n\r\nThis is an example of an \"Only What You Gave Me\" remix, where tracks from the original song are used in new and interesting ways to change how the song sounds and feels. As you listen, consider the following:\r\n\r\n- Notice the tempo of the song - how fast or slow certain instruments sounds. How does that affect how the song feels?\r\n- Notice how the vocals are used in the background of the song rather than the center of attention. How does that affect how the song feels?",
